data.description:
Discover comfort and convenience in this delightful home at 1114 Pack Avenue. Recently refreshed with fresh paint and newly replaced flooring, this residence exudes a welcoming ambiance throughout.

The thoughtfully designed layout features carpet only in the bedrooms, providing a cozy retreat. The kitchen boasts gas appliances, a rare treat in this area, ensuring both efficiency and style for your culinary endeavors.

Situated on a corner lot, this home offers a sense of space and privacy. Its prime location places it across the street from Mae Stevens Early Learning Academy and a nearby church.
